attendance: Tracks attendance at events, linking members to specific events. (Samples: link_to_event: [rec2N69DMcrqN9PJC, rec5XDvJLyxDsGZWc, recEVTik3MlqbvLFi]; link_to_member: [rec28ORZgcm1dtqBZ, recD078PnS3x2doBe, recEFd8s6pkrTt4Pz])
budget: Manages event budgets, categorizing expenses and tracking remaining funds. (Samples: budget_id: [rec0QmEc3cSQFQ6V2, rec1bG6HSft7XIvTP, rec1z6ISJU2HdIsVm]; category: [Advertisement, Food, Speaker Gifts]; event_status: [Closed, Open, Planning])
event: Stores information about upcoming and past events, including dates and locations. (Samples: event_id: [rec0Si5cQ4rJRVzd6, rec0akZnLLpGUloLH, rec0dZPcWXF0QjNnE]; event_name: [March Meeting, Officers meeting - January, Spring Elections]; event_date: [2020-03-10T12:00:00, 2020-01-14T09:30:00, 2019-11-24T09:00:00])
expense: Logs and tracks expenses related to events, including costs and approvals. (Samples: expense_id: [rec017x6R3hQqkLAo, rec1nIjoZKTYayqZ6, rec1oMgNFt7Y0G40x]; expense_description: [Post Cards, Posters, Water, Cookies, Pizza]; expense_date: [2019-08-20, 2019-10-08, 2019-09-10])
income: Records income received from various sources, such as dues and fundraising. (Samples: income_id: [rec0s9ZrO15zhzUeE, rec7f5XMQZexgtQJo, rec8BUJa8GXUjiglg]; date_received: [2019-10-17, 2019-09-04, 2019-10-08]; source: [Dues, Fundraising, School Appropration])
major: Lists available majors, including department and college information. (Samples: major_id: [rec06DF6vZ1CyPKpc, rec09LedkREyskCNv, rec0Eanv576RhQllI]; major_name: [Outdoor Product Design and Development, Agricultural Communication, Fisheries and Aquatic Sciences]; department: [Watershed Sciences Department, Economics and Finance Department])
member: Stores information about organization members, including contact details and positions. (Samples: member_id: [rec1x5zBFIqoOuPW8, rec280Sk7o31iG0Tx, rec28ORZgcm1dtqBZ]; first_name: [Angela, Grant, Luisa]; last_name: [Sanders, Gilmour, Guidi])
zip_code: Maintains a database of zip codes, including type and location information. (Samples: type: [Unique, Standard, PO Box]; city: [Holtsville, Adjuntas, Aguada]; county: [Suffolk County, Adjuntas Municipio, Aguada Municipio])
